    </SqlDataSource>
    <SqlDataSource Name="GPS_souradnice" ComponentName="sqlDataSource2">
      <Connection Name="postgreSqlConnection" FromAppConfig="true" />

        <Sql>select "gps_souradnice"."id","gps_souradnice"."Lon","gps_souradnice"."Lat","gps_souradnice"."Name" from "Mapy"."gps_souradnice"</Sql>
      </Query>

      <CalculatedFields>
